Prevents npm from running lifecycle scripts during install (preinstall, install, postinstall, etc.)
ignore-scripts=true
Blocks packages with suspicious subdependencies to prevent dependency attacks
block-exotic-subdeps=true
Requires packages to be at least 24 hours old before installation
minimum-release-age=1440
Only allows package upgrades, prevents downgrades to vulnerable versions
trust-policy=no-downgrade
Ignore trust downgrades for packages older than 7 days to reduce false positives
trust-policy-ignore-after=10080